Question-3(31-5-2021)
Draw this Pattern ðŸ‘‡

    *
   * * 
  * * *
 * * * *
* * * * *

solution--->
line = int(input("Enter no. of lines : "))
s = " "
for i in range(line):
	for j in range(line - i - 1):
		print(s,end="")
	for k in range(i + 1):
		print("*",end=s)
	print()
   
